Sugatas of the Five Families: bde gshegs rigs lnga — mainly in Vajrayāna contexts, the sugatas of the five
                                families: Vairocana for the Sugata (or Buddha) family; Akṣobhya for the Vajra family; Ratnasambhava for the Ratna (Jewel) family; Amitābha for the Padma (Lotus) family;
                                and Amoghasiddhi for the Karma (Activity) family. They are also associated with the five skandhas, five directions, and so forth.
